#

Honey Glazed Grilled Salmon

25 min
$20
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleoHigh Protein

Cuisine:

AmericanSeafood

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

EasyHealthyGrilledQuick

Description

Deliciously sweet and savory salmon fillets grilled to perfection, drizzled with a honey glaze.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 4 (6 oz)
  • honey: 1/4 cup
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • chopped parsley (for garnish): optional
